headline: Amphenol (APH) Stock Target Raised Despite AI Revenue Dip
summary: Amphenol Corporation (NYSE:APH) ranks among the best growth stocks to buy for the next 10 years. On July 25, Truist Securities maintained its Buy rating on Amphenol Corporation (NYSE:APH) and boosted its price target from $102 to $126.
